  <!-- EN: amulet soup -->
  <RI_Drug_TalismanWater.label>符水</RI_Drug_TalismanWater.label>
  <!-- EN: A bowl of clear water infused with the ashes of a burned charm. Fine sediment lingers at the bottom, and it emits a faintly calming presence.\n\nWhen consumed, it grants immunity to wound infections and intestinal illnesses for one day, non-addictive. -->
  <RI_Drug_TalismanWater.description>一碗加入烧尽符纸的清水，有少许沉淀，散发着令人心安的气息。\n\n饮用后在一天内可免疫伤口感染和肠道疾病，没有成瘾性。</RI_Drug_TalismanWater.description>
  
